(2382, 9, 'new_paragraph_9_new_title', 'The Wisdom Of the Past, a Strong Vision For the Future'),
(2383, 9, '_new_paragraph_9_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(2384, 9, 'new_paragraph_9_new_content', 'The story of John E. Brownlee is as much about progressive thinking and innovation as it is about passion and dedication. Not only did he establish one of Alberta''s most successful law practices, he served two terms as Premier of Alberta, he created and shaped the cooperative movement and the creation of member cooperatives across Western Canada, he created and ultimately led the United Grain Growers, and he ultimately foresaw that the future of Alberta and Albertans lay in the resource wealth that ought to belong to all of its citizens. It is not an exaggeration to state that much of the prosperity that Alberta enjoys today can be traced back to the vision that Mr. Brownlee had for Alberta both during and well after he held public office. His vision is one of the legacies that still lives within the walls of Brownlee LLP, the firm which proudly bears Mr. Brownlee''s name.'),
