(3196, 330, 'bio', 'Jill advises private sector clients, municipalities and other public sector clients on their corporate and commercial legal matters. She has extensive experience drafting and negotiating contracts for a variety of matters, including: the development and licensing of intellectual property, construction contracts, service contracts, and consulting contracts. Jill''s experience also includes acting for numerous clients in asset and share acquisitions and dispositions, amalgamations, and pipeline acquisitions. She also has intensive experience with matters relating to the development of, protection of, and transfer of intellectual property.'),
