(6683, 488, 'ne_content', 'Brownlee LLP is pleased to announce that Canadian Lawyer Magazine has listed Brownlee LLP as one of the top ten law firms in western Canada.\r\n\r\nThe list is the result of a survey that queried lawyers from across the nation asking them what western regional firms had the most exemplary regional service coverage, legal expertise, service excellence, client base, and notable mandates.\r\n\r\nOf the ten law firms listed by Canadian Lawyer Magazine, Brownlee was one of only five with their offices located in Alberta. The article highlights the firm’s culture of camaraderie and mentions a couple notable mandates, including our work on the Regional Municipality of Wood Buffalo in several major oil sands regulatory proceedings and our work with the Province of Alberta during its development of the Calgary Courts Center.\r\n\r\nThe full story can be read <a href="http://www.canadianlawyermag.com/Best-in-the-West.html">here.</a>'),
