(6881, 523, 'new_paragraph_0_new_content', 'Brownlee LLP is pleased to announce that we are now sending updates, bulletins and other helpful information through our E-News Bulletin System. This will permit easier and faster communication with you regarding emerging and important issues affecting you, our client. We will also provide links to prior publications, cases, past presentations, bios, e-mail and contact information for our team members as well as upcoming events, seminars and much, much more.\r\n\r\nPlease review a summary of our available bulletins and sign up to receive, free of charge, those of your choice.'),
