(7235, 577, '_ne_title', 'field_531fb61d778a4'),
(7236, 577, 'ne_content', 'The  much-­anticipated  decision  in  the  case  of Sparrowhawk  v.  Zapoltinsky  was  released  in  late January.    Readers  of   our  October  bulletin  may recall  that  the  primary  issue  in  Sparrowhaw was whether the Plaintiff''s temporomandibular joint (TMJ) injury was subject to the small tissue injury cap.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/brownlee-dev/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Sparrowhawk-vs-Zapoltinsky-Case-Comment.pdf">View PDF Article</a>\r\nMay 2012'),
