(8143, 658, 'representative_work', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Kelley has advised on, drafted, and negotiated numerous oil and gas agreements, development agreements, and other similar agreements and policies, as well as advised on offsite levies and other cost recovery mechanisms for municipalities throughout the province;</li>\r\n	<li>Kelley has appeared before administrative tribunals, the Municipal Government Board, the Alberta Court of Queen''s Bench, and the Alberta Court of Appeal on various matters including planning and development appeals and inter-municipal disputes;</li>\r\n	<li>Kelley worked as an in-house environmental and operations lawyer for a major multi-national pipeline company, advising on environmental policies and management, remediation, and environmental investigation; and</li>\r\n	<li>Kelley has advised on, drafted, and reviewed numerous land use bylaws, statutory plans and general municipal bylaws for municipalities throughout the province.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
