(9291, 690, 'bio', '<div>\r\n\r\nJill''s practice consists of advising and representing clients with respect to matters relating to commercial real estate and involves all aspects of commercial property transactions. Specific practice areas include the acquisition, disposition and financing of commercial real estate, and leasing of office, industrial and retail space (for both landlords and tenants). She is also involved in municipal commercial transactions including acquisitions, dispositions, leasing, rights-of-way, easements and restrictive covenants.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h1></h1>'),
