(9579, 698, 'bio', 'Roger assists lenders, mortgage brokers and mortgage servicers in structuring complex commercial loans and financings and prepares the necessary security documents, opinions and related documentation to secure such loans. Based upon his expertise and many years of experience in commercial lending, enforcement and re-structuring, he is able to create structures that ensure the maximum protection to lenders while encouraging the completion of transactions in a reasonable and timely manner.\r\n\r\nRoger also provides advice and assistance to buyers and sellers of commercial properties of all types including office, industrial, retail and multi-residential.\r\n\r\nHe has extensive experience in relation to condominiums both in terms of the creation and development of all types of condominium projects (including phased and mixed-use developments) and in relation to condominium governance and operation. In this regard, Roger led the team that revised the Condominium Property Act and Regulations in 2002.\r\n\r\nFinally, Roger provides legal and business advice to assist in corporate and commercial transactions, acquisitions and contracts both in terms of the purchase and sale of operating businesses and in relation to strategic and legal advice for major contractual negotiations.'),
(9580, 698, '_bio', 'field_5323822abc024'),
(9581, 698, 'representative_work', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Roger acts on behalf of major banks, insurance companies, pension funds, commercial mortgage brokers and private mortgage funds in relation to over 100 commercial financing transactions each year ranging in value from a million dollars to hundreds of millions of dollars;</li>\r\n	<li>He has also structured mortgage assumptions and negotiated with Canada Mortgage and Housing Corporation and lender groups to facilitate the conversion of large real estate companies into Real Estate Investment Trusts with properties throughout Canada;</li>\r\n	<li>Roger advises lenders and borrowers with respect to insolvency, mortgage enforcement and mortgage workouts and restructurings with the input and assistance of members of our insolvency and commercial litigation groups; and</li>\r\n	<li>Roger has provided advice to clients in relation to major business transactions including the purchase, sale and financing of businesses as well as strategic advice on complex negotiations.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(9582, 698, '_representative_work', 'field_532382ccbc029'),
(9583, 698, 'memberships', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Member, Law Society of Alberta</li>\r\n	<li>Member, Canadian Bar Association</li>\r\n</ul>'),
