(9977, 714, 'new_paragraph_0_new_title', 'Shareholder Disputes & Oppression Claims'),
(9978, 714, '_new_paragraph_0_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(9979, 714, 'new_paragraph_0_new_content', 'Brownlee lawyers will help both shareholders and directors in shareholder disputes.\r\n\r\nOur clients seek our advice when attempting to obtain oppression remedies and enforcement of their rights under Alberta''s<em> Business Corporations Act</em> or Unanimous Shareholder Agreements. We assist clients with share buyouts, receiving of shareholders loans and resolving corporate conflicts between two 50% shareholders.'),
(9980, 714, '_new_paragraph_0_new_content', 'field_531d701b6e41a'),
(9981, 714, 'new_paragraph_1_new_title', 'ADVISORY SERVICES'),
(9982, 714, '_new_paragraph_1_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(9983, 714, 'new_paragraph_1_new_content', 'Brownlee lawyers are well versed in the <em>Business Corporations Act</em>, which sets out the rights and obligations of shareholders and directors and protects minority shareholders rights.\r\n\r\nClients consult with Brownlee to help them achieve various outcomes; as a result, Brownlee has worked with chartered business valuators and utilized mediation and court process to resolve disputes and enforce a client''s rights.'),
(9984, 714, '_new_paragraph_1_new_content', 'field_531d701b6e41a'),
