(10017, 718, 'new_paragraph_0_new_title', 'Professional Liability & Disciplinary Matters'),
(10018, 718, '_new_paragraph_0_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(10019, 718, 'new_paragraph_0_new_content', 'Brownlee LLP represents various professionals appearing in disciplinary proceedings before their governing colleges. Brownlee helps clients prepare responses to complaints, guides them through disciplinary hearings and appeals, and successfully defends professionals in lawsuits alleging failure to meet professional standards. Whether our clients are confronted with disciplinary issues that require them to face their governing colleges or liability issues that have resulted from the issuing of a lawsuit, Brownlee’s qualified lawyers are capable of providing advice that advance their interests.\r\n\r\nBrownlee''s professional clients include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>psychologists</li>\r\n	<li>social workers</li>\r\n	<li>physical therapists</li>\r\n	<li>occupational therapists</li>\r\n	<li>pharmacists</li>\r\n	<li>land appraisers</li>\r\n	<li>dentists</li>\r\n	<li>emergency medical technicians</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>PROFESSIONAL COLLEGES</h2>'),
(10020, 718, '_new_paragraph_0_new_content', 'field_531d701b6e41a'),
(10021, 718, 'new_paragraph_1_new_title', 'PROFESSIONAL COLLEGES'),
(10022, 718, '_new_paragraph_1_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(10023, 718, 'new_paragraph_1_new_content', 'In addition to representing individuals appearing before governing colleges, Brownlee has also acquired experience advising various professional colleges involved in professional disciplinary hearings. Brownlee’s lawyers capably advise professional colleges on the proper rules and procedures required to insure that a hearing is carried out in a away that minimizes the chance of error and a resulting appeal.'),
