(10065, 721, 'new_paragraph_0_new_title', 'Oil & Gas'),
(10066, 721, '_new_paragraph_0_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(10067, 721, 'new_paragraph_0_new_content', 'Brownlee LLP''s Oil &amp; Gas Law department offers a comprehensive range of services and experienced lawyers with expertise in various aspects of energy law from production and marketing through to regulatory processes. We act on behalf of government entities, producers, royalty owners and oil and gas companies throughout Alberta and Western Canada.\r\n\r\nOur lawyers have completed work with energy sector clients to develop:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>licenses</li>\r\n	<li>sales contracts for natural gas, crude oil, natural gas liquids and coal</li>\r\n	<li>partnerships</li>\r\n	<li>financing</li>\r\n	<li>joint ventures and resource development agreements</li>\r\n	<li>acquisitions and mergers</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe have represented a broad range of clients involved in the exploration, production, marketing and transportation of crude oil, natural gas, natural gas liquids, sulphur and coal.\r\n\r\nOther services we offer include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>arranging export licenses</li>\r\n	<li>advising on natural gas supply and transportation contracts</li>\r\n	<li>advising on treaty lands</li>\r\n	<li>advising on takeovers</li>\r\n	<li>advising on competition law</li>\r\n	<li>due diligence</li>\r\n	<li>advising on exploration and production contracts</li>\r\n	<li>advising on partnership agreements and joint venture projects</li>\r\n	<li>advising on construction and plant operating agreements</li>\r\n	<li>negotiating and drafting natural resource leases</li>\r\n	<li>sourcing financing and security projects</li>\r\n	<li>debt restructuring</li>\r\n	<li>project financing</li>\r\n	<li>drafting loan and security agreements</li>\r\n</ul>'),
