(10074, 722, '_new_paragraph_0_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(10075, 722, 'new_paragraph_0_new_content', 'Brownlee lawyers defend clients who face regulatory charges stemming from workplace incidents resulting in injury or death.\r\n\r\nWe commonly represent organizations such as:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>construction firms</li>\r\n	<li>construction project owners</li>\r\n	<li>municipalities</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAlberta has become much more aggressive in charging individuals and companies who do not comply with occupational health and safety legislation. Brownlee is experienced in assessing the defence of a company and defending such charges.'),
(10076, 722, '_new_paragraph_0_new_content', 'field_531d701b6e41a'),
(10077, 722, 'new_paragraph_1_new_title', 'ADVISORY SERVICES'),
(10078, 722, '_new_paragraph_1_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(10079, 722, 'new_paragraph_1_new_content', 'Brownlee lawyers are knowledgeable of the health and safety measures that help prevent workplace injuries and ensure companies are complying with their safety obligations. We work with our clients to develop and implement these measures for the safety of their workers and in order to avoid or defend occupational health and safety charges.'),
