(10393, 742, 'new_paragraph_0_new_title', 'Commercial Transactions'),
(10394, 742, '_new_paragraph_0_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(10395, 742, 'new_paragraph_0_new_content', 'Our business clients understand the value of utilizing time and resources efficiently and effectively. They are continually looking for ways to enhance their ability to respond to business opportunities and challenges in order to maximize profitability. At Brownlee LLP, our long history of practice in commercial transactions provides the strong legal foundation necessary for supporting the endeavors of our clients.\r\n\r\nExamples of how the experience of our commercial team at Brownlee LLP can be used for the benefit of our clients when dealing with organizations of all sizes and with commercial transactions of all levels of complexity include the following:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>acquiring a business;</li>\r\n	<li>selling a business;</li>\r\n	<li>franchising;</li>\r\n	<li>negotiating and drafting commercial leases;</li>\r\n	<li>advising on intellectual property issues;</li>\r\n	<li>conforming to financing requirements;</li>\r\n	<li>negotiating and drafting licensing, distribution and service agreements;</li>\r\n	<li>facilitating tax-planned business reorganizations;</li>\r\n	<li>drafting employment agreements; and</li>\r\n	<li>negotiating and drafting collective agreements.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIn these situations, our clients will include business owners and operators that can be:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>sole proprietorships;</li>\r\n	<li>partnerships;</li>\r\n	<li>private corporations;</li>\r\n	<li>publicly traded corporations;</li>\r\n	<li>financial institutions and other commercial lenders;</li>\r\n	<li>various levels of government (including First Nation governments); and</li>\r\n	<li>non-profit organizations.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nClose collaboration between our clients and our Commercial Team members is critical and our team members make themselves available to assist as and when needed in order to help our clients achieve their objectives.'),
(10396, 742, '_new_paragraph_0_new_content', 'field_531d701b6e41a'),
(10397, 742, 'new_paragraph', '1'),
(10398, 742, '_new_paragraph', 'field_531d56646e418'),
(10399, 743, '_edit_last', '1'),
(10400, 743, '_edit_lock', '1395259251:1'),
(10401, 743, 'new_paragraph_0_new_title', 'Commercial Litigation & Enforcement'),
(10402, 743, '_new_paragraph_0_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(10403, 743, 'new_paragraph_0_new_content', 'Brownlee LLP represents its clients in commercial disputes of various types including:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>real estate transactions</li>\r\n	<li>construction contracts</li>\r\n	<li>franchise contracts</li>\r\n	<li>product liability</li>\r\n	<li>supplies and services contracts</li>\r\n	<li>confidential property rights</li>\r\n	<li>condominium disputes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBrownlee also offers insurance litigation services. For more information, <a title="Insurance Litigation" href="http://www.brownleelaw.com/practice-areas/195-insurance">click here.</a>\r\n\r\nIn addition, we help our clients enforce contractual rights in scenarios including:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>security enforcement and mortgage foreclosures</li>\r\n	<li>landlord and tenant disputes</li>\r\n	<li>development agreements</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe serve a variety of clients, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>entrepreneurs</li>\r\n	<li>small to mid-size companies and large corporate entities</li>\r\n	<li>lenders</li>\r\n	<li>landlords</li>\r\n	<li>municipalities</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(10404, 743, '_new_paragraph_0_new_content', 'field_531d701b6e41a'),
(10405, 743, 'new_paragraph_1_new_title', 'ADVISORY SERVICES'),
(10406, 743, '_new_paragraph_1_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(10407, 743, 'new_paragraph_1_new_content', 'We help our clients by making sure that they have an extensive understanding of their position and that they understand the litigation process fully, including its timing and costs.\r\n\r\nBrownlee will assess the client''s position at an early stage and coordinate a strategy to try and achieve the client''s objectives through negotiation, alternative dispute resolution, or by way of arbitration or trial if necessary.'),
(10408, 743, '_new_paragraph_1_new_content', 'field_531d701b6e41a'),
(10409, 743, 'new_paragraph', '2'),
(10410, 743, '_new_paragraph', 'field_531d56646e418'),
(10411, 744, '_edit_last', '1'),
(10412, 744, '_edit_lock', '1395259294:1'),
(10413, 744, 'new_paragraph_0_new_title', 'Commercial Lending & Financing'),
(10414, 744, '_new_paragraph_0_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(10415, 744, 'new_paragraph_0_new_content', 'Brownlee LLP operates one of the largest commercial lending practices in Western Canada. We take great pride in our reputation as problem solvers and deal closers. Our expertise in the field of commercial lending has resulted in many meaningful relationships with clients who consider our lawyers and staff to be valuable members of their team. We add value to commercial lending transactions by assisting in the creation of workable born structures and by streamlining the documentation and funding process\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Our lender clients include:</li>\r\n	<li>chartered banks</li>\r\n	<li>life insurance companies</li>\r\n	<li>major pension funds</li>\r\n	<li>mortgage investment corporations</li>\r\n	<li>private lenders</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIn addition, we frequently provide advice to borrowers relating to the negotiation and structuring of credit facilities with their lender.'),
(10416, 744, '_new_paragraph_0_new_content', 'field_531d701b6e41a'),
(10417, 744, 'new_paragraph_1_new_title', 'STRATEGIC ADVISOR TO MAJOR LENDERS'),
(10418, 744, '_new_paragraph_1_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(10419, 744, 'new_paragraph_1_new_content', 'When acting for lenders, we prefer to provide early-stage advice regarding the structuring of loans and loan security. Once the lender and borrower agree to business terms, our focus shifts to completing the transaction quickly and efficiently.'),
(10420, 744, '_new_paragraph_1_new_content', 'field_531d701b6e41a'),
(10421, 744, 'new_paragraph_2_new_title', 'STRATEGIC ADVISOR TO BUSINESS BORROWERS'),
(10422, 744, '_new_paragraph_2_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(10423, 744, 'new_paragraph_2_new_content', 'When acting for borrowers, we help structure our client''s credit facilities with a view to satisfying the lender''s requirements while allowing our client the maximum amount of flexibility in the continued operation of their business.'),
(10424, 744, '_new_paragraph_2_new_content', 'field_531d701b6e41a'),
(10425, 744, 'new_paragraph_3_new_title', 'RESOLVING ISSUES'),
(10426, 744, '_new_paragraph_3_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(10427, 744, 'new_paragraph_3_new_content', 'Our Commercial Lending Team can help both lenders and borrowers in matters relating to:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>security enforcement</li>\r\n	<li>receiverships</li>\r\n	<li>bankruptcy</li>\r\n	<li>insolvency</li>\r\n	<li>loan workouts and restructurings</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWhen dealing with these types of situations, we use strategies and solutions that resolve matters quickly and efficiently.'),
(10428, 744, '_new_paragraph_3_new_content', 'field_531d701b6e41a'),
(10429, 744, 'new_paragraph', '4'),
(10430, 744, '_new_paragraph', 'field_531d56646e418'),
(10431, 745, '_edit_last', '1'),
(10432, 745, '_edit_lock', '1395259329:1'),
(10433, 745, 'new_paragraph_0_new_title', 'Commercial Leasing'),
(10434, 745, '_new_paragraph_0_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(10435, 745, 'new_paragraph_0_new_content', 'Brownlee has extensive experience in dealing with all types of clients respecting the development, lease, finance and disposition of leased space. We also act for matters involving all types of properties, including:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Office space;</li>\r\n	<li>Industrial space;</li>\r\n	<li>Retail space; and</li>\r\n	<li>Vacant land to be developed and leased.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nAs such, Brownlee LLP understands all sides of the commercial leasing equation. We know what the Landlords are looking for and typically agree on. We know what Tenant''s motivations are and what they typically need. We know and understand what the financier requires in order to secure its loan in leased space.\r\n\r\nFurther, we have extensive experience in litigating commercial leasing matters, on behalf of both landlord and tenant. This involves outright litigation as well as acting in mediations and arbitrations of commercial leasing matters.\r\n\r\nOur knowledge of the differences that exist between large clients and small clients on all sides of the equation enables us to better anticipate the other side. This permits Brownlee to effectively serve our client to tell them what is obtainable, what is reasonable and how to obtain the best deal.'),
(10436, 745, '_new_paragraph_0_new_content', 'field_531d701b6e41a'),
(10437, 745, 'new_paragraph_1_new_title', 'TYPES OF CLIENTS'),
(10438, 745, '_new_paragraph_1_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(10439, 745, 'new_paragraph_1_new_content', 'We act for local, national and international property developers, management companies, REITs, investors and international, national, institutional and small users of commercial properties.\r\n\r\nThe below is just a small sample of the types of clients that we act for, on the Landlord side, the Tenant side and the financier side:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Shopping mall owners;</li>\r\n	<li>Office building owners;</li>\r\n	<li>Warehouse owners;</li>\r\n	<li>Governments and public bodies who lease space;</li>\r\n	<li>Institutional clients who need to lease space;</li>\r\n	<li>Large industrial tenants;</li>\r\n	<li>Large residential landlords;</li>\r\n	<li>Grocery store chains;</li>\r\n	<li>Land developers;</li>\r\n	<li>Businesses looking to lease commercial space;</li>\r\n	<li>Mortgage lenders who finance the development of commercial space.</li>\r\n</ol>'),
(10440, 745, '_new_paragraph_1_new_content', 'field_531d701b6e41a'),
(10441, 745, 'new_paragraph_2_new_title', 'WHAT WE DO FOR YOU'),
(10442, 745, '_new_paragraph_2_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(10443, 745, 'new_paragraph_2_new_content', 'It all depends what you need from us and when you need us to get involved. We are frequently involved with:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Preparation and negotiation of terms of Offers to Lease;</li>\r\n	<li>Preparation and negotiation of the Lease Document;</li>\r\n	<li>Negotiating and addressing all matters related to the assignment of leasehold interests and subleases;</li>\r\n	<li>Advocating for our clients through the lease relationship;</li>\r\n	<li>As counsel for our clients, litigate, mediate and arbitrate disputes between Landlord and Tenant.</li>\r\n</ol>'),
(10444, 745, '_new_paragraph_2_new_content', 'field_531d701b6e41a'),
(10445, 745, 'new_paragraph', '3'),
(10446, 745, '_new_paragraph', 'field_531d56646e418'),
(10447, 746, '_edit_last', '1'),
(10448, 746, '_edit_lock', '1395259350:1'),
(10449, 746, 'new_paragraph_0_new_title', 'Bankruptcy & Insolvency'),
(10450, 746, '_new_paragraph_0_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(10451, 746, 'new_paragraph_0_new_content', 'Brownlee LLP lawyers help advise clients as they deal with the insolvency or financial distress of a business. Whether that scenario involves receivership, bankruptcy or<em> Company Creditors Arrangement Act</em> (CCAA) proceedings, Brownlee will be willing and ready to participate in a way that effectively serves your needs.\r\n\r\nWe provide guidance to entities on all sides of insolvency scenarios.\r\n\r\nOrganizations we help include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>businesses and business owners with financial problems and restructuring</li>\r\n	<li>organization that commonly participate in insolvency situations, such as account firms, lenders and bankruptcy trustees</li>\r\n	<li>receivers</li>\r\n	<li>municipalities</li>\r\n	<li>creditors, both secured and unsecured</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(10452, 746, '_new_paragraph_0_new_content', 'field_531d701b6e41a'),
(10453, 746, 'new_paragraph_1_new_title', 'ADVISORY SERVICES'),
(10454, 746, '_new_paragraph_1_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(10455, 746, 'new_paragraph_1_new_content', 'At Brownlee, we take the time to fully understand a client''s position before advising on options and developing and implementing strategies that effectively serve the clients objectives.'),
(10456, 746, '_new_paragraph_1_new_content', 'field_531d701b6e41a'),
