(10482, 748, '_new_paragraph_1_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(10483, 748, 'new_paragraph_1_new_content', 'At Brownlee, we understand the many dynamic legal issues surrounding self-government and how these issues affect the day to day governance and business operations of First Nations. For clients actively engaged in issues pertaining to Aboriginal law, Brownlee LLP can provide assistance and advice on many relevant topics including:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>self-government</li>\r\n	<li>aboriginal rights</li>\r\n	<li>constitutional law &amp; rights</li>\r\n	<li>federal and provincial government structures</li>\r\n	<li>treaty rights</li>\r\n	<li>the Charter of Rights and Freedoms</li>\r\n	<li>business</li>\r\n	<li>real estate</li>\r\n	<li>construction and procurement</li>\r\n	<li>infrastructure and utilities</li>\r\n	<li>litigation</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(10484, 748, '_new_paragraph_1_new_content', 'field_531d701b6e41a'),
