(11202, 782, '_new_paragraph_10_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(11203, 782, 'new_paragraph_10_new_content', 'Several Brownlee LLP lawyers have received judicial appointments, including Ernest J. Walter, Q.C., now a Judge of the Provincial Court of Alberta and formerly Chief Judge of the Provincial Court of Alberta; Peter T. Costigan, Q.C. formerly a Justice of the Court of Queen''s Bench of Alberta, now a Justice of the Court of Appeal of Alberta; Paul G. Sully, Q.C., appointed a Judge of the Provincial Court of Alberta; Leo J. Burgess, Q.C., appointed a Judge in the Provincial Court of Alberta; and Bruce R. Garriock, Q.C., appointed a Judge in the Provincial Court of Alberta. Many Brownlee LLP lawyers have written scholarly articles on various aspects of the law, and have fulfilled speaking engagements on legal subjects.  Read more about these by clicking on events and legal information resources.\r\nTo discover the scope of legal services we offer, click on practice areas.  To learn more about the individual lawyers and the area of their legal expertise, please click on lawyers.  To read our wide range of articles, publications and other legal materials, please click on legal information resources.  To find out how to contact us, and to become more familiar with our firm, click on about us.'),
