(11244, 784, '_new_paragraph_0_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(11245, 784, 'new_paragraph_0_new_content', 'Brownlee supports various local, regional, and national charities on an ongoing basis through sponsorships and donations; however our biggest collaboration is that of our fall United Way Campaign. Brownlee supports this cause annually and in 2013 made a total contribution of $60,177.50, our biggest single contribution yet! Our total funds raised are now at an astounding $512,800.50'),
