(11249, 784, 'new_paragraph_1_new_title', 'MAKE-A-WISH FOUNDATION'),
(11250, 784, '_new_paragraph_1_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(11251, 784, 'new_paragraph_1_new_content', 'The mission of Make-A-Wish® Canada is to grant the wishes of children with life-threatening medical conditions to enrich the human experience with hope, strength and joy.\r\n\r\nBrownlee LLP is committed to giving back to the community and is happy to announce our partnership with Make-A-Wish® which will support wish granting efforts in the province of Alberta. We will keep you posted on our "Wish Stories" as they develop and invite you to learn more about this foundation and get involved by visiting <a href="http://www.makeawish.ca/">www.makeawish.ca</a>.'),
