(11281, 784, 'new_paragraph_6_new_content', 'Crossroads House is a service that provides housing and social support to approximately 18 women. These women have often left an abusive situation or life on the street and are trying to make a transition to a healthy, mainstream lifestyle.  Crossroads House provides women with a safe and welcoming environment to help them move confidently into an improved home situation. Women are also given access to counselling and are assisted with developing skills to ensure that a positive lifestyle can be maintained.\r\n\r\nBrownlee works every year to provide a Christmas hamper for every individual currently living in the house. These hampers will provide each woman with greatly needed toiletries and clothing that will aid her with her transition.'),
