(11701, 810, '_new_paragraph_1_new_title', 'field_531d6fe36e419'),
(11702, 810, 'new_paragraph_1_new_content', 'Construction projects are complicated. Risks abound. There are many issues that arise from the start to the finish of any project. Some of these issues are legal in nature. Brownlee LLP’s “Constructive Thinking” newsletter, published by Brownlee LLP’s Construction Law Team, covers the relevant issues facing those involved in construction projects--from tendering procedures to bonding and insurance coverage, from project delivery models to construction insolvency. Brownlee LLP’s “Constructive Thinking” newsletter will keep you up to date on current issues and trends with the goal of enhancing your prudent risk management.'),
