(274, 1, '2014-03-14 05:36:02', '2014-03-14 05:36:02', 'Our summer positions are open to both first and second year law students. Brownlee''s Edmonton office traditionally participates in the on-campus interviews at the University of Alberta. That said, we very much welcome applications from students who are attending law school in Calgary, or out of province. We would encourage all students to submit their application materials to our firm by no later than 2 weeks prior to the commencement of the "Recruitment Period" for summer students, as defined by the Law Society of Alberta. If an in-person meeting is not possible, we can certainly arrange for a telephone or teleconference interview.', 'Edmonton Summer Student On-Campus Interview', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'edmonton-summer-student-on-campus-interview', '', '', '2014-03-14 05:36:02', '2014-03-14 05:36:02', '', 0, 'http://localhost/brownlee/?post_type=career_links&#038;p=274', 12, 'career_links', '', 0),
